<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

<p>At Felix's Paper Mill, we are committed to protecting the privacy and security of our customers' personal information. This policy describes the types of information we may collect from you, how we use it, and how we keep it secure.</p>

<h2>Information We Collect</h2>

<p>We may collect the following types of information from our customers:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Name</li>
  <li>Email address</li>
  <li>Postal address</li>
  <li>Phone number</li>
  <li>Order history</li>
</ul>

<h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>

<p>We use the information we collect from you to:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Process and fulfill your orders</li>
  <li>Communicate with you about your orders and other relevant information</li>
  <li>Improve our products and services</li>
  <li>Send you promotional materials and special offers (if you opt in to receive them)</li>
</ul>

<h2>Security Measures</h2>

<p>We take the security of your personal information very seriously. We use a variety of physical, technical, and administrative safeguards to protect your information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure.</p>

<h2>Third-Party Services</h2>

<p>We may use third-party services to help us process your orders, communicate with you, or analyze our website traffic. These third-party services may collect information about you as part of their services, and we may share your information with them as necessary to provide our services to you. We take steps to ensure that any third-party services we use are trustworthy and have appropriate security measures in place.</p>

<h2>Your Rights</h2>

<p>You have the right to request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal information that we collect and maintain. You can contact us at any time to exercise these rights.</p>

<h2>Changes to this Policy</h2>

<p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time as our data handling practices evolve. We will notify you of any significant changes to this policy and obtain your consent before using your personal information in new ways.</p>
